Nkituaak


1  Kaji eshomo ilo lino linyor,

iyie enaisul inkituaak?

Kaji eibelekenyakine olinyor lino alo,

pee kitum iyiook aaing'oru ninye tenebo iyie?

Enkitok


2  Etadoyie olanyor lai alo enkurma enye,

ine neitobirieki isonkoyoni,

alo airrita iluaat oo ntare enyena too nkurman,

nesotu ntapuka.


3  Ara nanu eno lanyor lai, ore olanyor lai naa olalai;

eirritita ntare enyena too neetii intapuka.

Osinkolio le miet

Olee


4  Ira iyie sidai anaa Tirsah,

olanyor lai

ira sidai anaa Yerusalem,

keitureisho anaa enjore naata inankan.


5  Imbelekenya inkonyek inono intung'uayioki,

amu kaaitanyamal ninche nanu,

ore ilpapit linono netiu anaa iluaat oo nkineji,

naadou to loshong'ishong'i le Gilead.


6  Etiu ilala linono anaa iluaat oo supeni e kerra,

nena naetuo ailepu te nkisujata,

neeta pooki ilmao, meetae nabo natua olkuoo.


7  Ore ntakul inono netiu anaa isashat olng'anayioi oji kukumanka,

tiatua ina arasha naimulumulieki enkomom.


8  Eetae nkaiguanak ntomoni ile,

neetae nkapiak intomoni isiet,

o nkaisiaayiak nemeikenayu.


9  Na turkulu ai, enemeeta eleyiata ai,

naa nabo ake,

ina nanyor ng'otonye enye,

ina kirotet te ng'otonye.

Etoduaa ninye nkaisiayiak neipot ninye aajo enashipa;

ore nkaiguanak o nkapiak neisis sii ninche ninye.


10  “Aing'ae ele otiu enduaata enye anaa entadekenya,

newang anaa olapa, anaa enkolong,

neitureisho anaa enjore naata inankan.


11  Atadoyie alo ine netii enkurma oo lng'anayio

aing'or nena tapuka naatii oerata,

aing'uraa tenaa keimarrimar ilkeek loo sabibu,

tenaa keitapuka ilng'anayio ooji kukumanka.


12  Ore apa eton mayiolo naayau oltau lai,

tiatua engarri oo mbartan tembata olkitok lai.”

Enkitok


13  Tushukunye, tushukunye iyie lo Shulami,

tushukunye tushukunye pee kitum aing'ura iyie.

Ainyoo peyie ing'or iyie ilo Shulami,

anaa oloipidipid aiguran te dukuya injorin are?

